{"product_id":"vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic conditioner, specially designed to strengthen and moisturise damaged hair, leaving it soft and smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy extract (invigorating), wheat germ oil (protecting), organic extracts of lavender (soothing), sage (strengthening) and mallow (moisturising).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply after shampooing to wet hair. Massage gently into hair and on scalp. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Betaine*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Tocopherol*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901055078727,"sku":null,"price":32.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml-654164.jpg?v=1739897176","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}